{"type": "article", "id": 17040, "title": "衣帽架", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-04T07:10:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115211pr2q9oRidvzAe06h.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师常常在衣帽架上做结构变化，产品设计师 Arthur Xin 带来的衣帽架，只用木制的小鸟或者毛毛虫代替原本的挂钩，让衣架有了一片生趣。小鸟和毛毛虫都有一个可以勾住的自然幅度，不过，真要将衣服挂在绿色的毛毛虫挂钩上，不少人心理一定是拒绝的。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144243I6A3Ynmks7ZqORGP.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"735\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442446txwFiZPnaBXsqCz.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"735\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144244JWdVAPcDqE9w2CSU.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"735\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}